title: Robotech Battlecry
description:
Robotech: Battlecry is a video game set in the Robotech universe, the first video 

game successfully released for the franchise. It was developed by Vicious Cycle 

Software and published by the now-defunct TDK Mediactive, in association with Harmony 

Gold USA. With a story focused on new characters created for the game and with guest 

appearances of main characters Rick Hunter, Roy Fokker, Lisa Hayes and a part of one 

in-game mission directly centered on Lynn Minmei, it somewhat follows the Robotech 

continuum.
